@startuml Manual_Time_Setting
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam BoxPadding 10

title Manual Time Setting Sequence

participant "User" as User
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "app.js" as AppJS
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "ESP32" as ESP32
participant "STM32" as STM32
participant "DS3231" as DS3231

note over User,Browser: User adjusts time picker

User -> Browser: Select date in calendar
activate Browser
Browser -> AppJS: Click event
activate AppJS
AppJS -> AppJS: timePickerDay = selectedDay
AppJS -> Browser: renderCalendar()\nHighlight selected date
deactivate Browser
deactivate AppJS

User -> Browser: Click hour UP/DOWN
activate Browser
Browser -> AppJS: adjustTime('hour', delta)
activate AppJS
AppJS -> AppJS: timePickerHour += delta\nWrap 0-23
AppJS -> Browser: updateTimeDisplay()\nShow HH:MM:SS
deactivate Browser
deactivate AppJS

User -> Browser: Click minute UP/DOWN
activate Browser
Browser -> AppJS: adjustTime('min', delta)
activate AppJS
AppJS -> AppJS: timePickerMinute += delta\nWrap 0-59
AppJS -> Browser: updateTimeDisplay()
deactivate Browser
deactivate AppJS

User -> Browser: Click second UP/DOWN
activate Browser
Browser -> AppJS: adjustTime('sec', delta)
activate AppJS
AppJS -> AppJS: timePickerSecond += delta\nWrap 0-59
AppJS -> Browser: updateTimeDisplay()
deactivate Browser
deactivate AppJS

User -> Browser: Click "Set Time Manually"
activate Browser
Browser -> AppJS: Click event
deactivate Browser
activate AppJS

AppJS -> AppJS: Read time picker state\nyear, month, day,\nhour, minute, second

AppJS -> AppJS: Create Date object\ndate = new Date(year, month, day,\nhour, minute, second)

AppJS -> AppJS: Get Unix timestamp\ntimestamp = date.getTime() / 1000

AppJS -> AppJS: Add UTC+7 offset\ntimestampWithOffset = timestamp + 7*3600

AppJS -> AppJS: Build command\n"SET TIME {timestampWithOffset}"

AppJS -> AppJS: Check isMqttConnected

alt MQTT Connected
    AppJS -> MQTT: Publish(stm32Command,\n"SET TIME X", qos=1)
    activate MQTT
    
    MQTT -> ESP32: Forward command
    activate ESP32
    deactivate MQTT
    ESP32 -> STM32: UART transmit\n{"cmd":"SET TIME","value":X}
    activate STM32
    deactivate ESP32
    
    STM32 -> DS3231: I2C write\nSet RTC registers
    activate DS3231
    DS3231 --> STM32: Write complete
    deactivate DS3231
    deactivate STM32
    
    STM32 -> ESP32: UART confirm
    activate ESP32
    ESP32 -> MQTT: Publish(systemState)
    activate MQTT
    deactivate ESP32
    MQTT -> AppJS: Confirmation
    deactivate MQTT
    
    AppJS -> AppJS: addStatus("Manual time set:\n{datetime} (UTC+7)")
else MQTT Not Connected
    AppJS -> AppJS: addStatus("ERROR:\nMQTT not connected")
end

AppJS -> AppJS: Update local device clock\ndeviceClockMs = timestamp * 1000\ndeviceClockSetAtMs = Date.now()

AppJS -> AppJS: startDeviceClockTicker()
AppJS -> Browser: Update #footerTime
activate Browser
deactivate Browser

AppJS -> User: Time updated
deactivate AppJS

@enduml